{"tha-ap538:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap538:0.2":"Kaccayanavagga ","tha-ap538:0.3":"Bahiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap538:1.1":"“Ito satasahassamhi, ","tha-ap538:1.2":"kappe uppajji nayako; ","tha-ap538:1.3":"Mahappabho tilokaggo, ","tha-ap538:1.4":"namena padumuttaro. ","tha-ap538:2.1":"Khippabhinnassa bhikkhussa, ","tha-ap538:2.2":"gunam kittayato mune; ","tha-ap538:2.3":"Sutva udaggacittoham, ","tha-ap538:2.4":"karam katva mahesino. ","tha-ap538:3.1":"Datva sattahikam danam, ","tha-ap538:3.2":"sasissassa mune aham; ","tha-ap538:3.3":"Abhivadiya sambuddham, ","tha-ap538:3.4":"tam thanam patthayim tada. ","tha-ap538:4.1":"Tato mam byakari buddho, ","tha-ap538:4.2":"‘etam passatha brahmanam; ","tha-ap538:4.3":"Patitam padamule me, ","tha-ap538:4.4":"cariyam paccavekkhanam. ","tha-ap538:5.1":"Hemayannopacitangam, ","tha-ap538:5.2":"avadatatanuttacam; ","tha-ap538:5.3":"Palambabimbatambottham, ","tha-ap538:5.4":"setatinhasamam dijam. ","tha-ap538:6.1":"Gunathamabahutaram, ","tha-ap538:6.2":"samuggatatanuruham; ","tha-ap538:6.3":"Gunoghayatanibhutam, ","tha-ap538:6.4":"pitisamphullitananam. ","tha-ap538:7.1":"Eso patthayate thanam, ","tha-ap538:7.2":"khippabhinnassa bhikkhuno; ","tha-ap538:7.3":"Anagate mahaviro, ","tha-ap538:7.4":"gotamo nama hessati. ","tha-ap538:8.1":"Tassa dhammesu dayado, ","tha-ap538:8.2":"oraso dhammanimmito; ","tha-ap538:8.3":"Bahiyo nama namena, ","tha-ap538:8.4":"hessati satthu savako’. ","tha-ap538:9.1":"Tada hi tuttho vutthaya, ","tha-ap538:9.2":"yavajivam mahamune; ","tha-ap538:9.3":"Karam katva cuto saggam, ","tha-ap538:9.4":"agam sabhavanam yatha. ","tha-ap538:10.1":"Devabhuto manusso va, ","tha-ap538:10.2":"sukhito tassa kammuno; ","tha-ap538:10.3":"Vahasa samsaritvana, ","tha-ap538:10.4":"sampattimanubhomaham. ","tha-ap538:11.1":"Puna kassapavirassa, ","tha-ap538:11.2":"atthamentamhi sasane; ","tha-ap538:11.3":"Aruyha selasikharam, ","tha-ap538:11.4":"yunjitva jinasasanam. ","tha-ap538:12.1":"Visuddhasilo sappanno, ","tha-ap538:12.2":"jinasasanakarako; ","tha-ap538:12.3":"Tato cuta panca jana, ","tha-ap538:12.4":"devalokam agamhase. ","tha-ap538:13.1":"Tatoham bahiyo jato, ","tha-ap538:13.2":"bharukacche puruttame; ","tha-ap538:13.3":"Tato navaya pakkhando, ","tha-ap538:13.4":"sagaram appasiddhiyam. ","tha-ap538:14.1":"Tato nava abhijjittha, ","tha-ap538:14.2":"gantvana katipahakam; ","tha-ap538:14.3":"Tada bhisanake ghore, ","tha-ap538:14.4":"patito makarakare. ","tha-ap538:15.1":"Tadaham vayamitvana, ","tha-ap538:15.2":"santaritva mahodadhim; ","tha-ap538:15.3":"Supparapattanavaram, ","tha-ap538:15.4":"sampatto mandavedhito. ","tha-ap538:16.1":"Daruciram nivasetva, ","tha-ap538:16.2":"gamam pindaya pavisim; ","tha-ap538:16.3":"Tadaha so jano tuttho, ","tha-ap538:16.4":"‘arahayamidhagato. ","tha-ap538:17.1":"Imam annena panena, ","tha-ap538:17.2":"vatthena sayanena ca; ","tha-ap538:17.3":"Bhesajjena ca sakkatva, ","tha-ap538:17.4":"hessama sukhita mayam’. ","tha-ap538:18.1":"Paccayanam tada labhi, ","tha-ap538:18.2":"tehi sakkatapujito; ","tha-ap538:18.3":"Arahahanti sankappam, ","tha-ap538:18.4":"uppadesim ayoniso. ","tha-ap538:19.1":"Tato me cittamannaya, ","tha-ap538:19.2":"codayi pubbadevata; ","tha-ap538:19.3":"‘Na tvam upayamaggannu, ","tha-ap538:19.4":"kuto tvam araha bhave’. ","tha-ap538:20.1":"Codito taya samviggo, ","tha-ap538:20.2":"tadaham paripucchi tam; ","tha-ap538:20.3":"‘Ke va ete kuhim loke, ","tha-ap538:20.4":"arahanto naruttama’. ","tha-ap538:21.1":"‘Savatthiyam kosalamandire jino, ","tha-ap538:21.2":"Pahutapanno varabhurimedhaso; ","tha-ap538:21.3":"So sakyaputto araha anasavo, ","tha-ap538:21.4":"Deseti dhammam arahattapattiya’. ","tha-ap538:22.1":"Tadassa sutva vacanam supinito, ","tha-ap538:22.2":"Nidhimva laddha kapanoti vimhito; ","tha-ap538:22.3":"Udaggacitto arahattamuttamam, ","tha-ap538:22.4":"Sudassanam datthumanantagocaram. ","tha-ap538:23.1":"Tada tato nikkhamitvana ‘satthuno, ","tha-ap538:23.2":"Sada jinam passami vimalananam’; ","tha-ap538:23.3":"Upecca rammam vijitavhayam vanam, ","tha-ap538:23.4":"Dije apucchim ‘kuhim lokanandano’. ","tha-ap538:24.1":"‘Tato avocum naradevavandito, ","tha-ap538:24.2":"Puram pavittho asanesanaya so; ","tha-ap538:24.3":"Sasova khippam munidassanussuko, ","tha-ap538:24.4":"Upecca vandahi tamaggapuggalam’. ","tha-ap538:25.1":"Tatoham tuvatam gantva, ","tha-ap538:25.2":"savatthim puramuttamam; ","tha-ap538:25.3":"Vicarantam tamaddakkhim, ","tha-ap538:25.4":"pindattham apihagidham. ","tha-ap538:26.1":"Pattapanim alolakkham, ","tha-ap538:26.2":"pacayantam pitakaram; ","tha-ap538:26.3":"Sirinilayasankasam, ","tha-ap538:26.4":"ravidittiharananam. ","tha-ap538:27.1":"Tam samecca nipaccaham, ","tha-ap538:27.2":"idam vacanamabravim; ","tha-ap538:27.3":"‘Kupathe vippanatthassa, ","tha-ap538:27.4":"saranam hohi gotama’. ","tha-ap538:28.1":"‘Panasantaranatthaya, ","tha-ap538:28.2":"pindaya vicaramaham; ","tha-ap538:28.3":"Na te dhammakathakalo’, ","tha-ap538:28.4":"iccaha munisattamo. ","tha-ap538:29.1":"Tada punappunam buddham, ","tha-ap538:29.2":"ayacim dhammalalaso; ","tha-ap538:29.3":"Yo me dhammamadesesi, ","tha-ap538:29.4":"gambhiram sunnatam padam. ","tha-ap538:30.1":"Tassa dhammam sunitvana, ","tha-ap538:30.2":"papunim asavakkhayam; ","tha-ap538:30.3":"Parikkhinayuko santo, ","tha-ap538:30.4":"aho satthanukampako. ","tha-ap538:31.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap538:31.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap538:31.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap538:32.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap538:32.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap538:32.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap538:33.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap538:33.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap538:33.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap538:34.1":"Evam thero viyakasi, ","tha-ap538:34.2":"bahiyo daruciriyo; ","tha-ap538:34.3":"Sankarakute patito, ","tha-ap538:34.4":"bhutavitthaya gaviya. ","tha-ap538:35.1":"Attano pubbacariyam, ","tha-ap538:35.2":"kittayitva mahamati; ","tha-ap538:35.3":"Parinibbayi so thero, ","tha-ap538:35.4":"savatthiyam puruttame. ","tha-ap538:36.1":"Nagara nikkhamanto tam, ","tha-ap538:36.2":"disvana isisattamo; ","tha-ap538:36.3":"Daruciradharam dhiram, ","tha-ap538:36.4":"bahiyam bahitagamam. ","tha-ap538:37.1":"Bhumiyam patitam dantam, ","tha-ap538:37.2":"indaketuva patitam; ","tha-ap538:37.3":"Gatayum sukkhakilesam, ","tha-ap538:37.4":"jinasasanakarakam. ","tha-ap538:38.1":"Tato amantayi sattha, ","tha-ap538:38.2":"savake sasane rate; ","tha-ap538:38.3":"‘Ganhatha netva jhapetha, ","tha-ap538:38.4":"tanum sabrahmacarino. ","tha-ap538:39.1":"Thupam karotha pujetha, ","tha-ap538:39.2":"nibbuto so mahamati; ","tha-ap538:39.3":"Khippabhinnanamesaggo, ","tha-ap538:39.4":"savako me vacokaro. ","tha-ap538:40.1":"Sahassamapi ce gatha, ","tha-ap538:40.2":"anatthapadasanhita; ","tha-ap538:40.3":"Ekam gathapadam seyyo, ","tha-ap538:40.4":"yam sutva upasammati. ","tha-ap538:41.1":"Yattha apo ca pathavi, ","tha-ap538:41.2":"tejo vayo na gadhati; ","tha-ap538:41.3":"Na tattha sukka jotanti, ","tha-ap538:41.4":"adicco na pakasati. ","tha-ap538:42.1":"Na tattha candima bhati, ","tha-ap538:42.2":"tamo tattha na vijjati; ","tha-ap538:42.3":"Yada ca attana vedi, ","tha-ap538:42.4":"munimonena brahmano. ","tha-ap538:43.1":"Atha rupa arupa ca, ","tha-ap538:43.2":"sukhadukkha vimuccati’; ","tha-ap538:43.3":"Iccevam abhani natho, ","tha-ap538:43.4":"tilokasarano muni”. ","tha-ap538:44.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma bahiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap538:45.1":"Bahiyattherassapadanam chattham. "}